{"tid":1296413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要】正視港人健康問題","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:32:19.000Z","uid":259980,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c6b0239055498a5d5787921d1a72f5b218c688","tid":1296413,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"自6月以嚟，香港人雖然做多咗運動，但係要做到真正嘅身體健康，除咗運動，均衡嘅飲食亦都非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n進食一d垃圾快餐食品，例如薯條、魚柳包之類嘅食品，唔單止會引導三高問題，仲會增加罹患癌症嘅風險，大大增加香港人嘅死亡率。<br />\n<br />\n在此，我希望各位連登仔、文宣組可以助我發起「港人健康運動」，用圖片嘅方式將快餐食物嘅壞處，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1各種心血管疾病、肥胖問題<br />\n<br />\n2必要時可以加入世衛、衛生處嘅研究<br />\n<br />\n3千其唔好胡亂加入陽痿、性無能之類嘅病<br />\n<br />\n4食物衛生問題同樣影響健康，可以將歷年嚟有開衛生問題嘅新聞整合<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要宣揚出去，周街airdrop比人，幫助更多香港人培養健康飲食習慣，直至快餐店痛改前非。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，要健康！"},{"pid":"7ad022f46b027d37182f50a1d49fd5dcdd0629f2","tid":1296413,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01a75cd2c4b12baefc7d30d387bd9584e36be1d9","tid":1296413,"uid":77277,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n<br />\n其實香港人食夠蛋白質再講<br />\n<br />\n太多人唔食早餐或者食空氣包或沙爹牛面"},{"pid":"ba357d0772abd33abfa92aefbc649b98e5855b31","tid":1296413,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1477b455edde528ead38f5e8bf39879564b95dc","tid":1296413,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"3餐雞胸"},{"pid":"42ef5ff0bf273ef6d69f994c5faf53127d595f7a","tid":1296413,"uid":271049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"戒高糖份飲品同台式茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e2c828659b7aad5b79e1b4aee1d45f837605d6","tid":1296413,"uid":201303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"拰"},{"pid":"38f90ddbed66af3b716746c47ba0bb11a6624f16","tid":1296413,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.assignmentpoint.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Globalization-impact-on-McDonalds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.assignmentpoint.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F03%2FGlobalization-impact-on-McDonalds.jpg&h=60a84022&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"766bdcfcbd26bc6ab902459408110488c4f8ead9","tid":1296413,"uid":270642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"嬲到死唔落 係米可以減肥"},{"pid":"f5d785a25e67d6db519f44ce1dd0d0034bf36ed0","tid":1296413,"uid":270642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"766bdcfcbd26bc6ab902459408110488c4f8ead9","tid":1296413,"uid":270642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"嬲到死唔落 係米可以減肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"食*"}]}